        <title type="html"><![CDATA[Découvrir Docusaurus pour faire un site statique]]></title>
        <id>decouvrir-docusaurus</id>
        <link href="https://benoitlathiere.github.io/build/blog/decouvrir-docusaurus"/>
        <updated>2022-04-10T19:05:48.057Z</updated>
        <summary type="html"><![CDATA[Docusaurus est un framework développé par Facebook et qui permet de générer un site statique. Le Javascript moderne permet de nombreux modes de développement, et la génération de site statique (Static Site Generator, SSG) pour héberger les pages sur des serveurs sans moteur de script (ni PHP, ni Java, ...).]]></summary>
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>Docusaurus est un framework développé par Facebook et qui permet de générer un site statique. Le Javascript moderne permet de nombreux modes de développement, et la génération de site statique (<em>Static Site Generator, SSG</em>) pour héberger les pages sur des serveurs sans moteur de script (ni PHP, ni Java, ...). </p><p>Quel intérêt ? un site statique est beaucoup plus rapide à afficher dans les navigateurs (pas de script ou de base de données côté serveur),  ce qui est idéal si vous avez des pages qui ne changent peu (pas exemple un blog ou un site de documentation). </p><p>Evidemment, ça ne se prête pas à un site de e-commerce en perpétuel modification (certaines parties peuvent être générés par avance mais les pages présentées présentent toujours des données calculées en direct).</p><ol><li>nouvelle clé ssh dans ~/.ssh/ : <code>ssh-keygen -t ed25519 -C "your_email@example.com"</code></li><li>puis <code>start-ssh-agent</code></li><li>puis ajout de clé publique dans Github -&gt; profile/setting -&gt; SSH keys -&gt; nouvelle clé:</li><li>coller contenu fichier <em>.pub</em>.</li></ol><p>Si Github-pages n'arrive pas à déployer ou si le site ne fonctionne pas, vérifier la branche dans le dépôt : "settings / Pages / Source".</p><p>L'état du déploiement est disponible dans "Github.com &gt; \&lt;repo<!-- -->&gt;<!-- --> &gt; Actions".</p><h2 class="anchor anchorWithStickyNavbar_LWe7" id="déploiement">Déploiement<a class="hash-link" href="#déploiement" title="Lien direct vers le titre">​</a></h2><div class="language-powershell codeBlockContainer_Ckt0 theme-code-block" style="--prism-color:#393A34;--prism-background-color:#f6f8fa"><div class="codeBlockContent_biex"><pre tabindex="0" class="prism-code language-powershell codeBlock_bY9V thin-scrollbar"><code class="codeBlockLines_e6Vv"><span class="token-line" style="color:#393A34"><span class="token plain">cmd /C 'set "GIT_USER=&lt;login&gt; USE_SSH=true" &amp;&amp; yarn deploy'</span><br></span></code></pre><div class="buttonGroup__atx"><button type="button" aria-label="Copier le code" title="Copier" class="clean-btn"><span class="copyButtonIcons_eSgA" aria-hidden="true"><svg class="copyButtonIcon_y97N" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M19,21H8V7H19M19,5H8A2,2 0 0,0 6,7V21A2,2 0 0,0 8,23H19A2,2 0 0,0 21,21V7A2,2 0 0,0 19,5M16,1H4A2,2 0 0,0 2,3V17H4V3H16V1Z"></path></svg><svg class="copyButtonSuccessIcon_LjdS" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M21,7L9,19L3.5,13.5L4.91,12.09L9,16.17L19.59,5.59L21,7Z"></path></svg></span></button></div></div></div><p><code>Running "git push" command failed. Does the GitHub user account you are using have push access to the repository?</code> : mettre une clé dans le dépôt avec droit d'écriture.</p><p>Si erreur d'accès au dépôt :</p><div class="language-bash codeBlockContainer_Ckt0 theme-code-block" style="--prism-color:#393A34;--prism-background-color:#f6f8fa"><div class="codeBlockContent_biex"><pre tabindex="0" class="prism-code language-bash codeBlock_bY9V thin-scrollbar"><code class="codeBlockLines_e6Vv"><span class="token-line" style="color:#393A34"><span class="token punctuation" style="color:#393A34">..</span><span class="token plain">.</span><br></span><span class="token-line" style="color:#393A34"><span class="token plain"></span><span class="token punctuation" style="color:#393A34">[</span><span class="token plain">ERROR</span><span class="token punctuation" style="color:#393A34">]</span><span class="token plain"> Deployment of the build output failed.</span><br></span><span class="token-line" style="color:#393A34"><span class="token plain"></span><span class="token punctuation" style="color:#393A34">[</span><span class="token plain">ERROR</span><span class="token punctuation" style="color:#393A34">]</span><span class="token plain"> Error: Running </span><span class="token string" style="color:#e3116c">"git push"</span><span class="token plain"> </span><span class="token builtin class-name">command</span><span class="token plain"> failed. Does the GitHub user account you are using have push access to the repository?</span><br></span><span class="token-line" style="color:#393A34"><span class="token plain">error Command failed with </span><span class="token builtin class-name">exit</span><span class="token plain"> code </span><span class="token number" style="color:#36acaa">1</span><span class="token plain">.</span><br></span><span class="token-line" style="color:#393A34"><span class="token plain"></span><span class="token punctuation" style="color:#393A34">..</span><span class="token plain">.</span><br></span></code></pre><div class="buttonGroup__atx"><button type="button" aria-label="Copier le code" title="Copier" class="clean-btn"><span class="copyButtonIcons_eSgA" aria-hidden="true"><svg class="copyButtonIcon_y97N" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M19,21H8V7H19M19,5H8A2,2 0 0,0 6,7V21A2,2 0 0,0 8,23H19A2,2 0 0,0 21,21V7A2,2 0 0,0 19,5M16,1H4A2,2 0 0,0 2,3V17H4V3H16V1Z"></path></svg><svg class="copyButtonSuccessIcon_LjdS" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M21,7L9,19L3.5,13.5L4.91,12.09L9,16.17L19.59,5.59L21,7Z"></path></svg></span></button></div></div></div><p>Vérifier que :</p><ul><li>Vérifier qu'une paire de clés SSH (publique + privée) est dans <em>~/.ssh/</em>, et coller le contenu de la clé publique (fichier <em>.pub</em>) dans le compte <em>github.com &gt; settings &gt; deploy keys</em>.</li><li>Enlever les vieux serveurs de <em>~/.ssh/known<!-- -->_<!-- -->hosts</em> par <code>ssh-keygen -R &lt;server&gt;</code> (in fichier <em>know<!-- -->_<!-- -->hosts.old</em> est créé).</li><li>Faire un <code>git clone git@github.com:&lt;login&gt;/&lt;repo&gt;.git</code> du dépôt dans un dossier test et vérifier que le client git accède au dépôt, il va éventuellement demander une autorisation d'accès () :</li></ul><div class="language-bash codeBlockContainer_Ckt0 theme-code-block" style="--prism-color:#393A34;--prism-background-color:#f6f8fa"><div class="codeBlockContent_biex"><pre tabindex="0" class="prism-code language-bash codeBlock_bY9V thin-scrollbar"><code class="codeBlockLines_e6Vv"><span class="token-line" style="color:#393A34"><span class="token plain">The authenticity of </span><span class="token function" style="color:#d73a49">host</span><span class="token plain"> </span><span class="token string" style="color:#e3116c">'github.com (140.82.121.4)'</span><span class="token plain"> can't be established.</span><br></span><span class="token-line" style="color:#393A34"><span class="token plain">ED25519 key fingerprint is SHA256:+DiY3wqssfdSFSDFsdfSFSfgfgdGDFGdfgCOqU.</span><br></span><span class="token-line" style="color:#393A34"><span class="token plain">This key is not known by any other names</span><br></span><span class="token-line" style="color:#393A34"><span class="token plain">Are you sure you want to </span><span class="token builtin class-name">continue</span><span class="token plain"> connecting </span><span class="token punctuation" style="color:#393A34">(</span><span class="token plain">yes/no/</span><span class="token punctuation" style="color:#393A34">[</span><span class="token plain">fingerprint</span><span class="token punctuation" style="color:#393A34">]</span><span class="token punctuation" style="color:#393A34">)</span><span class="token plain">? </span><span class="token function" style="color:#d73a49">yes</span><br></span></code></pre><div class="buttonGroup__atx"><button type="button" aria-label="Copier le code" title="Copier" class="clean-btn"><span class="copyButtonIcons_eSgA" aria-hidden="true"><svg class="copyButtonIcon_y97N" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M19,21H8V7H19M19,5H8A2,2 0 0,0 6,7V21A2,2 0 0,0 8,23H19A2,2 0 0,0 21,21V7A2,2 0 0,0 19,5M16,1H4A2,2 0 0,0 2,3V17H4V3H16V1Z"></path></svg><svg class="copyButtonSuccessIcon_LjdS" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M21,7L9,19L3.5,13.5L4.91,12.09L9,16.17L19.59,5.59L21,7Z"></path></svg></span></button></div></div></div><p>Configurer son compte SSH sur son poste :</p><div class="language-bash codeBlockContainer_Ckt0 theme-code-block" style="--prism-color:#393A34;--prism-background-color:#f6f8fa"><div class="codeBlockContent_biex"><pre tabindex="0" class="prism-code language-bash codeBlock_bY9V thin-scrollbar"><code class="codeBlockLines_e6Vv"><span class="token-line" style="color:#393A34"><span class="token function" style="color:#d73a49">git</span><span class="token plain"> config --global user.email </span><span class="token string" style="color:#e3116c">"you@example.com"</span><span class="token plain"></span><br></span><span class="token-line" style="color:#393A34"><span class="token plain"></span><span class="token function" style="color:#d73a49">git</span><span class="token plain"> config --global user.name </span><span class="token string" style="color:#e3116c">"Your Name"</span><span class="token plain"></span><br></span><span class="token-line" style="color:#393A34"><span class="token plain"></span><span class="token comment" style="color:#999988;font-style:italic">#git config --global http.sslverify false</span><span class="token plain"></span><br></span><span class="token-line" style="color:#393A34"><span class="token plain"></span><span class="token function" style="color:#d73a49">git</span><span class="token plain"> config --list</span><br></span></code></pre><div class="buttonGroup__atx"><button type="button" aria-label="Copier le code" title="Copier" class="clean-btn"><span class="copyButtonIcons_eSgA" aria-hidden="true"><svg class="copyButtonIcon_y97N" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M19,21H8V7H19M19,5H8A2,2 0 0,0 6,7V21A2,2 0 0,0 8,23H19A2,2 0 0,0 21,21V7A2,2 0 0,0 19,5M16,1H4A2,2 0 0,0 2,3V17H4V3H16V1Z"></path></svg><svg class="copyButtonSuccessIcon_LjdS" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M21,7L9,19L3.5,13.5L4.91,12.09L9,16.17L19.59,5.59L21,7Z"></path></svg></span></button></div></div></div>]]></content>
